# Guidelines
- Use consistent code formatting and linting.
- Prefer functional components and hooks in React.
- Keep components small and focused.
- Use TypeScript for type safety.
- Store reusable logic in the src/lib directory.
- Exclude build, cache, and node_modules directories from AI context.
- Follow best practices for Next.js 15 and React 19.
